  "url": "https://www.tamilmirror.lk/\u0b9a\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bcd/\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd-\u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd-\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8-\u0b86\u0bb3-\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1/175-299378",
  "time_ut": 1656425657,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u2019\u0b95\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd  \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc8 \u0b86\u0bb3 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bc1\u2019",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "'Wild law cannot rule the country'",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Opposition leader Sajid Premadasa has said that a country cannot be ruled by wild law and that democratic measures must be taken.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said this during a meeting with representatives of civil society organizations, representatives of various parties involved in the struggle and party leaders at the office of the Leader of the Opposition today (27).",
        "He called for a series of struggles in and around parliament for democratic victory, through which the people should be able to win.",
        "In particular, he said, their sole purpose was to establish democracy through the implementation of the 21st Amendment and the restrictions and equations that govern power.",
        "The Leader of the Opposition said that many parties involved in the struggle had submitted proposals to the Leader of the Opposition and that special attention would be paid to all the relevant proposals."
      ],
